      <title>美国财政部呼吁中国提高货币互换透明度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/us-treasury-calls-for-transparency-on-china-s-currency-swaps</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国财政部一名高级官员指出，中国的外汇互换额度缺乏透明度，并敦促国际货币基金组织谨慎对待将其简单地纳入发展中国家官方储备的计算中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/us-treasury-calls-for-transparency-on-china-s-currency-swaps</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 17:36:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波音公司考虑通过出售股票筹集至少 100 亿美元资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/boeing-said-to-weigh-raising-at-least-10-billion-selling-stock</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，波音公司正考虑通过发行新股筹集至少 100 亿美元，以补充因持续罢工而进一步耗尽的现金储备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/boeing-said-to-weigh-raising-at-least-10-billion-selling-stock</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 10:08:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗向以色列发射火箭弹 油价飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-1</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗向以色列发射火箭弹后，油价飙升，加大了该地区原油供应中断的风险。该地区原油产量占全球原油产量的三分之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-1</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 23:26:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
